### Create area
POST http://localhost:8080/api/areas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "areaName": "District 1",
  "areaLink": "district-1"
}

### Get by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/areas/1

### List areas (paged)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/areas?page=0&size=10

### Update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/areas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "areaName": "District 1 Updated",
  "areaLink": "district-1-updated"
}

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/areas/2


